'''''The African Who Wanted to Fly'''''  ( French   ) ni filime yo muri Gabon ya 2016 iyobowe na [[Samantha Biffot]] . Igice gishingiye kubuzima bwa Luc Bendza . Filime yakozwe mu ndimi ebyiri, [[Gishinwa|Igishinwa]] [[Igifaransa|n'Igifaransa]], kandi yari ifite insanganyamatsiko [[Icyongereza|y'icyongereza.]] 

== Umusaruro ==
'''''The African Who Wanted to Fly''''' yakozwe na Neon Rouge, afatanije na Theatre Company Theatre ( [[Ubufaransa]] ).  Scenese yafatiwe amashusho muri [[Gabon]], no mu Bushinwa. Umuziki wari ugizwe nindirimbo zishinwa. 

== Umugambi ==
Urebye filime Big Boss, umwana wo muri [[Gabon]] yavumbuye Kung Fu ahitamo kujya mu [[Ubushinwa|Bushinwa]] afite imyaka 15 gusa. Yize ko azaba umunyafrica wambere wize ibihangano bya Kung Fu. Ahinduka inararibonye muri yo.

== Kwerekanwa ==

* Iyi filime yarebwaga mu iserukiramuco rya sinema nyafurika muri kaminuza ya Duke ku ya 27 Gashyantare 2019. 
* ''Ku ya 19 Gicurasi 2017, Maysles Documentary Centre'' yerekanye filime mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya 24 rya New York muri New York. 
